ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This is an intensive course which requires dedication and hard work, as well as a high command of the language, and familiarity with history and culture of the region and period. However, once the student is prepared for the challenge, he will find it extremely rewarding. I highly recommend it to the serious student.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I always wanted to take a course like this and it was never offered.I am very glad that it finally happened, and with such exemplary quality, no less.
